{"title":"Must Watch: Kilian Bron’s Colors of Mexico with daring descent of active volcano","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/20/must-watch-kilian-brons-colors-of-mexico-with-daring-descent-of-active-volcano/","date":1634745659000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"572\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit-800x572.jpg\" alt=\"kilian bron colors of mexico steps\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit-800x572.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit-297x212.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit-120x86.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit-768x549.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091348/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-edit.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-275520\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Much to our delight, Commencal are continually churning out some of the best, most artfully shot mountain bike videos on the internet, many of which feature freerider Kilian Bron doing what he does best in some of the most beautiful places on the planet. Commencal and Kilian have knocked it out of the park again.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano.jpg\" alt=\"kilian bron colors of mexico descending active volcano\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091355/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-active-volcano-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The new edit, Colors of Mexico, takes footage from a month long road trip over this vast and incredibly diverse country, packing it into just 4.5 minutes of inspirational riding. Taking in active volcanoes, narrow staircases and alleys, crop mazes, train tracks, ancient monuments, and sweet sandy singletrack, Kilian Bron goes fast <em>everywhere</em>.</p><p>Colors of Mexico follows Kilian’s previous jaw-dropping edit<i>&nbsp;“<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/16/kilian-bron-follows-a-fire-lit-drone-through-cappadocia-in-follow-the-light/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Follow The Light</a>” </i>in which he famously rides the fairy chimneys of Cappadocia, Turkey, his GoPro footage of which earned him and Pierre Dupont $17,000 a piece in the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/12/19/gopros-hero9-black-million-dollar-highlight-video-doesnt-disappoint/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GoPro HERO9 Black Million Dollar video challenge</a>.</p><h2>Kilian Bron’s Colors of Mexico</h2><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/00PB3Ng5hhY?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><ul><li>Directed by: Pierre</li><li>Henni Film: Pierre Henni FPV</li><li>Drone: Cinematic Flow</li><li>Edit: Pierre Henni</li><li>Music &amp; Sound Edit: Leo Lunel</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091358/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-aqueduct.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091358/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-aqueduct.jpg\" alt=\"kilian bron colors of mexico aqueduct\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1143\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091358/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-aqueduct.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091358/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-aqueduct-297x212.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091358/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-aqueduct-800x572.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/20091358/kilian-bron-colors-of-mexico-riding-aqueduct-120x86.jpg 1